Titolo: SnowRunner

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: SnowRunner is a 2020 off-road simulation video game developed by Saber Interactive and published by Focus Home Interactive. SnowRunner has the player control off-road vehicles as they traverse between locations to complete objectives. Following on from Spintires and the sequel version MudRunner, the game was announced as MudRunner 2 in August 2018. Focus Home and Saber Interactive decided to re-reveal the title a year later as SnowRunner. The game features over 60 different vehicles and more than 15 sandbox locations.

